Finance::YahooJPN::Sym2Name version 0.01
========================================

 This module provides you functions to converts a Japanese stock
 symbol code to the name of company.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

 This module and the test script requires internet connection.

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.
 And,
 this module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Exporter
   Carp
   LWP::Simple
   Encode

